                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x9F1392D6<!--String: "You've seen that Peculiar Plumbird thing over by her nest, right? I know I'm supposed to give you the whole line about how there's all this history about Plumbirds blah blah, but being honest, I'm not into it. She's weird, it's weird, and I'm trying to keep my own thing going without having to talk about pinfeathers this and that. Like, find another hobby or something."--></T>
                  <T>0x9BF6F1B8<!--String: "The other day, Star got in a fight with Sara Chavez-Ralston! It was so, so funny. I mean I think I'm supposed to back my wife up and for sure I do, but it's just so hilarious when she feels like being petty and kicking up a ruckus. "--></T>
                  <T>0x8E09D1EF<!--String: "I know I'm kind of a mean Sim and not everyone's favorite, but Star and I really get each other, and running a Getaway together has been really good for our relationship. Maybe I should put more effort into being kinder now that success is giving me this boost of confidence."--></T>
